Two tiny MagicBathyNet Sentinel-2 sample tiles live here, used only by the
dashboard's "Load sample tile" button. Layout (matches MagicBathyNet):

  data/sample/
    agia_napa/
      img/s2/img_411.tif
      depth/s2/depth_411.tif
      norm_param_s2_an.txt
    puck_lagoon/
      img/s2/img_411.tif
      depth/s2/depth_411.tif
      norm_param_s2_pl.txt

These ~50 KB files are MagicBathyNet redistributables under CC-BY-NC-SA.
For full training, download the complete dataset from:
  https://zenodo.org/records/16753753
